Class PatternMatch<E>

java.lang.Object
org.variantsync.diffdetective.preliminary.analysis.data.PatternMatch<E>
@Deprecated public class PatternMatch<E> extends Object
Deprecated.
Data class containing a single match of a pattern in a patch. Contains information about the feature mapping and the location of the match. There can be multiple PatternMatches per patch.
